==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Amalgamator
<hw>A*mal"ga*ma`tor</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who, or
that which, amalgamates. Specifically: A machine for separating precious
metals from earthy particles by bringing them in contact with a body of
mercury with which they form an amalgam.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Amalgamize</ent>⟦br⟧
